&lt;p&gt;This is not a traditional role with narrowly defined responsibilities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will join a cross-functional transformation squad focused on identifying inefficiencies, challenging legacy workflows, and implementing AI-powered solutions that create measurable business impact.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Some team members may come from technical backgrounds. Others from operations, product, analytics, project management, or completely different industries.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What matters the most:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;ability to solve real problems in a variety of different departments across the organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;be agile and forward-thinking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;not to be tied to legacy systems and processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;be innovative and propose creative solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;adaptability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for people who naturally ask: “Why do we still do it this way?” and then help build something new and better.&lt;/p&gt;
