&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Self-directed and sufficient&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable with ambiguity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong problem-solver with analytical thinking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to communicate clearly with both technical and non-technical teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously curious about AI and emerging technologies&lt;/li&gt;
